      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">6</infon>
        <offset>753</offset>
        <text>This selective lysis is due to the ammonium characteristics of the aminoclay and the electrostatic attraction between the clay nanoparticles and the algal cells.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">7</infon>
        <offset>915</offset>
        <text>In contrast, yellow loess clay, a recognized treatment for HABs, causes algal flocs with little cell lysis.
</text>
        <annotation id="T9">
          <infon key="brat-id">T9</infon>
          <infon key="type">Cause</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
